headline: GTA Online
subtitle: GTA Online Bonuses this Week: Premium Stunt Race (Sept 9 - 15)
content: This week's Premium Stunt Race features the popular ''Downtown Loop'', and is set to the Banshee 900R. True to its name with a series of loops, corkscrews and jumps set in downtown Los Santos, this Premium Stunt Race features payouts for the top 3 finishers and Triple RP for all participants. To hop right into the high-stakes action, enter via the Quick Job App or visit the yellow Premium Race blip at Legion Square.
